title: Exit Out Of The Rabbit Hole (The Gay Agenda Exposed) [2016]
description:
My film exposes the "Gay Agenda."   The Gay Agenda is everywhere in the media.  My film is intended to reach people that are gay and show them that Jesus Christ is the truth.  I'm hoping that they can see that homosexuality is a sinful lifestyle.  You aren't born gay, being gay is a lifestyle.  Second, my film is for people that think there is no gay agenda in the media.  The gay agenda is subtle and subversive and it's in all forms of media.  The gay agenda is to make people gay and accept being gay as normal.  This propaganda is being waged through the media, TV SHOWS, MOVIES, MUSIC... My film will show and expose this. 

"There is a way which seemeth right unto a man, but the end thereof are the ways of death."
Proverbs 14:12 

7 hour film

Please Be at least 18 to watch.

Please Seed for many days or even months
